prompt: A charming illustration of a Montmartre street scene. A street artist is depicted at work, capturing the lively atmosphere on canvas. In the foreground, a couple shares a bottle of wine at a small café, while a group of children play with a dog in the street. The Sacré-Cœur Basilica looms in the background, its domes shining in the sunlight. The engraving is done in a warm, earthy tone, evoking the bohemian spirit of the area.
revised_prompt: Generate an image of a lively street scene in Montmartre, Paris. A street artist, of South Asian descent and female, is fervently creating a masterpiece on canvas, capturing the bustle and energy of the environment. In the foreground, a couple of mixed descent, one being Hispanic and male, the other being Caucasian and female, happily share a bottle of wine at a petite café. A group of Black and Middle-Eastern children are joyously engaged in playing with a dog, creating a heartwarming spectacle on the street. In the backdrop, the domes of Sacré-Cœur Basilica are visible, basking gloriously under the bright sunlight. The entire illustration should radiate warmth and earthiness to channel the bohemian spirit of the area.
